    "description": "Positive-unlabeled convolutional neural networks for particle picking in cryo-electron micrographs.\n\nPipeline for particle picking in cryo-electron microscopy images using convolutional neural networks trained from positive and unlabeled examples.\n\nA pipeline for particle detection in cryo-electron microscopy images using convolutional neural networks trained from positive and unlabeled examples. Topaz also includes methods for micrograph denoising using deep denoising models.\n\nTopaz: particle picking with positive-unlabeled learning.\n\n||| COMMON LINK WITH (PUB. & NAME DIFFERENT) bio.tools/hapi (CSAIL.MIT.EDU), bio.tools/isobase (CSAIL.MIT.EDU), bio.tools/struct2net (CSAIL.MIT.EDU), bio.tools/partifold (CSAIL.MIT.EDU)",
